---
title: Smart Apricot Pork Salad with Lentils and Almonds
description: Sweet apricot spread works double duty in this smart recipe, brightening up the vinaigrette and also serving as a sweet-savoury glaze for the pork! Earthy lentils, crunchy almonds and creamy goat cheese make this a hearty salad you won't want to pass on.

